{"id": "chos047", "name": "Audio_Cell32_702_12_29", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[TV]"], "content": "<i>The attacks that occurred earlier in Node 08 have spread to Quadrant II's industrial district, causing widespread panic amongst the citizens. Besides more and more drones joining in on the attack, many eyewitnesses also pointed out that the Architects gathered at A.R.C. headquarters have become more dangerous...</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Criminal G"], "content": "Hey, what's going on here? We're not going to get attacked, are we?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Criminal J"], "content": "Let us out! I don't want to die here!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent P"], "content": "Shut up! Keep it down in there! Otherwise, you're gonna get it!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......\n......?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "Explosion"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent P"], "content": "<i>... *cough*... *cough*</i>... What the...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Drone]"], "content": "<i>Threat detected, initiating elimination.</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent P"], "content": "!? S***...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "It's done. Everyone get in there and make sure everyone's safe!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Gang Member"], "content": "You got it, Brother Fang!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent P"], "content": "Are you... from the Administration Bureau?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Ha? You kidding me?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["electric bust", "Electric Shock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent P"], "content": "WWAAAAHHHH!!! ... Ugh...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "You'll be fine ya dirty cop. This card opens the locks, right?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "Lock Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Criminal G"], "content": "Oh, oh oh. Comin' to save us?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Criminal J"], "content": "Yeah! ...Eh!?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Raises Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Anyone makes a move, and I blow your brains out.\n<font size=\"3.6\">GOT IT!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Criminal G", " Criminal J"], "content": "Y-Yeah!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Wonderful.\nI'm looking for Luis Pauline. Where is he?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "... That's me.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Ah, great.\n... Everyone, show your respect!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Gang Member"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Yes, sir! Sir, how are you, sir!</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Sorry to bother you, sir. We're here to get you outta here.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "... Ah, yes. Now I remember. I saw you at the funeral. You're one of Baro's...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "It's a long story... JOE got a plan together and everyone agreed on it. The gangs are now cooperating and are preparing to help the citizens.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "!? ... Diego agreed?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Diego's dead. He died in Baro's 03 branch.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "... Is that so...\nAnd why exactly are you protecting me?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "JOE predicted there'd be another attack, so he sent us here to protect you. It's a mess outside, we've got to be quick. Com' on, let's go.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "... No. I'll stay here. You guys head back.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Brother, the attack this time is totally different. If necessary, all citizens will need to be evacuated. JOE begged us to get you out of the restricted area before it's too late...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "Well... it doesn't matter.\nJOE probably told you that I'm in for homicide. Simon's father died at my hands.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "I got what I deserved. Even if I die, it's a life for a life. Not to mention that my daughter's gone as well. If I go down then I'll be able to join her. Nothing bad about that...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "... JOE told us that Simon's already back in Node 08, currently fighting with the enemy.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "!? Simon, he... he returned?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Yeah. Looks like he's doing everything he can to stop this.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Brother, us gang members have all made some mistakes. Some of us will never be able to atone for our crimes; we'll regret what we've done for the rest of our lives. Maybe you think it doesn't matter if you die, but if we can use the remainder of our time to do something good...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Brother?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "Watch out!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Drone]"], "content": "<i>Threat......tected...... <font size=\"1.6\">elimination......</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "Huff, puff... huff...\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Impressive. Took my gun that quick? And still shot with perfect accuracy...\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "... Take me to JOE.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Brother... get it?\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "You said it. After all, I'm still alive.\nI may be a piece of s***... but I ought I use this useless life for something good. It's about time I start helping others.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[テレビ]"], "content": "<i>先ほどNode08で発生した事件ですが、その被害は第二象限ビジネス街まで広がっており、周囲の住民の不安を煽っています。再び制御を失い暴走するドローンは増える一方で、目撃者によるとA.R.C.本部周辺に集まる人型ロボットはさらに危険と……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["犯罪者 G"], "content": "おい！なんだこれは。\nまさかここまで襲われたりしないよな？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["犯罪者 J"], "content": "ここから出してくれ！\nこんなところで死にたくない！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "うるさいぞ！静かにしろ！\nさもないとわかってるな！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "………\n……？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆発"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "ゲホッ……！ゴホッ！いったいなん……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ドローン]"], "content": "<i>脅威を検知しました。排除します。</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "！？しまっ……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "今だ！中に入って安全を確保しろ！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ヤクザ"], "content": "はい！Fang兄貴！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "お前たちは……管理局か？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "はぁ？何言ってんだ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["electric bust", "電撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "ぐああああ！！……ぐっ……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "もうお前に用はない。\nこのカードで鍵が開くんだな？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "鍵を開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["犯罪者 G"], "content": "あぁ……あぁ……！\nまさか俺たちを助けに？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["犯罪者 J"], "content": "よかった……なっ！？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃をかまえる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "動くな。動けば脳みそをぶち抜く。\n<font size=\"3.6\">聞こえてんのか！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["犯罪者 G、犯罪者 J"], "content": "はい！はいぃぃ！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "それでいい。\n……Luis Paulineはいるか？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……私だ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "よかった。\n……てめぇら頭下げろ！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ヤクザ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">はい！兄貴！\nお初にお目にかかります！</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "驚かせてすみません。\n兄貴を助けに来ました。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……あぁ。思いだした……葬式で見かけた。\nただ、お前はバローの人間じゃ……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "話せば長くなりますが……JOEの提案に全員が賛同して、今俺たちはみんな協力関係にあるんです。\n市民のために動こうということになりました。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？……Diegoが同意したのか？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Diegoは死にました。\n03のバロー支部で。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……そうだったのか……\nだが、なぜ私のようなやつを助けに？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "JOEのヤツがまた同じような暴走事件は起こるはずだって言うもんで、兄貴の安全を確保しに来ました。\n今外は滅茶苦茶です。\nさあ、こちらへ。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……いや、私はここに残ろう。\n君たちだけで帰ってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "兄貴……今回のはこれまでとは比べもんになんねぇデカさです。\n市民全員避難する必要が出てくる可能性もあります。\nJOEのヤツに頼まれたんだ。兄貴をここで死なせるわけにはいかない……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "いや……いいんだ。\nJOEから聞いてるだろう？\n私は殺人犯だ。\nSimonの父親を殺したのは私だ。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "私には罪を償う義務がある。\n死んだとしてもそれも宿命だろう。\nそれに、娘ももういない。\n死ねば、娘に会えるかもしれん……何も悪いことなんてない……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "……Simonという男がNode08へ戻ってきて、敵と交戦中だとJOEが言っていました。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？Simonが……帰ってきているのか？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "はい。\n全てを阻止すると決めたようです。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "兄貴、俺たちヤクザはこれまで大小色んな罪を犯してきました。\nもう罪をあがなう機会さえ残されてないやつもいる。\n一生後悔しながら生きていくしかないやつもいる。\n兄貴は死んでも構わねぇって思ってるかもしれねぇ。\nでも、生きてりゃまだやれることが……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "兄貴？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "危ない！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ドローン]"], "content": "<i>脅威を検……チ……<font size=\"1.6\">ハイジョ……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "はあっ……はっ……はっ……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "すげぇ……一瞬で俺の銃を奪って照準を……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……JOEのところへ連れて行ってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "兄貴……わかってくれたんですか。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "君の言うとおりだ。\n私はまだ生きている。\nクソみたいな命だが……誰かのために使おう。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[電視]"], "content": "<i>稍早於 Node 08 發生的攻擊事件，受災範圍已擴大到第二象限商業區，讓市民陷入巨大恐慌。除了越來越多無人機再度故障加入攻擊，不少目擊者亦指出，聚集在 A.R.C. 總部四周的人型機器人更加危險……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 G"], "content": "喂，這到底是怎麼回事？我們不會被攻擊吧？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 J"], "content": "快放我們走！我還不想死在這種地方！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "閉嘴！都給我安靜！否則有你們受的！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……。\n……？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "咳、咳，怎麼回……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>偵測到威脅，開始進行排除。</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "！？糟……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "搞定了，大家衝進去確保安全！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑幫人員"], "content": "是！Fang 哥！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "你們……是管理局的人嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "哈？傻了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["electric bust", "電擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "嗚啊啊啊啊！！……唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "沒你的事了，臭條子。這張卡就能開鎖了吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開鎖"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 G"], "content": "喔、喔喔，是來救我們的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 J"], "content": "太好了……噫！？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "誰敢亂動，老子就崩掉誰的腦袋。\n<font size=\"3.6\">聽清楚了沒有！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 G、罪犯 J"], "content": "是、是！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "很好。\n……我找 Luis Pauline，哪一位？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……是我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "啊，太好了。\n……全體，敬禮！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑幫人員"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">是！大哥好！</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "驚擾大哥了，我們是來救大哥出去的。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……對了，我想起來了，喪禮那天我有見過你。但你是 Baro 的人……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "說來話長……JOE 提出了一個計畫，受到大家的認同。現在黑幫已經彼此合作，也準備為了一般市民做點事。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？……Diego 也同意？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Diego 已經死了，死在 03 的 Baro 支部裡。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……是這樣嗎……\n那為什麼要來保護我這種人？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "JOE 那傢伙預測到會再有攻擊事件，才派我們來保護大哥安全。現在外面很混亂，我們得快點，來，和我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……不了，我待在這裡就好。你們回去吧。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥，這次攻擊和之前的規模不一樣，必要的話可能全體市民都得撤離。JOE 已經拜託我了，我不能讓大哥死在管制區裡頭……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "那也……沒關係。\nJOE 應該和你說了，我是個殺人犯。Simon 的父親就是死在我的手上。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "我罪有應得，就算死了也是一命償一命。何況現在女兒也走了，我下去就能和她團聚，沒什麼不好……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "……JOE 和我說，那位 Simon 已經回到了 Node 08，正在與敵人交戰中。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？Simon 他……他回來了？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "是，看來他決定要全力阻止這一切發生。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥，我們黑幫的人多少都犯過一些錯，有些人甚至已經沒有贖罪的機會，只能後悔一輩子。也許大哥覺得死了也無所謂，但如果能用剩餘的一條爛命做到更多……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "小心！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>偵測……到……<font size=\"1.6\">排除……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "呼、呼……呼……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "真厲害，一瞬間搶走我的槍並且瞄準……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……帶我去 JOE 那裡。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥……想通了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "就像你說的，我畢竟還活著。\n這條爛命……就用在幫助別人身上吧。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[TV]"], "content": "<i>앞전에 Node 08에서 발생한 테러 사건의 여파가 제2사분면의 상업 지구까지 미쳐 시민들이 공포에 떨고 있습니다. 이상 오류를 보이며 무차별 공격에 가담하고 있는 드론의 수가 조금씩 증가하고 있으며 A.R.C 본부 사방에 인간형 기체들이 집결하고 있다는 수많은 목격자들의 제보가 빗발치고 있...</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["범죄자 G"], "content": "어이, 이게 대체 어떻게 된 일이야? 우리를 공격한다는 얘긴 없었잖아?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["범죄자 J"], "content": "빨리 우리를 풀어줘! 이런 곳에서 죽고 싶지 않단 말이야!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 P"], "content": "닥쳐! 조용히들 해! \n안 그러면 정말 그렇게 만들어줄 테니까!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......\n......?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "폭발"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "! ?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 P"], "content": "쿨럭! 쿨럭! 이게 무슨...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[드론]"], "content": "<i>위협을 감지, 제거를 시작합니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 P"], "content": "! ? 그게 무슨 개소...\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사 공격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "지금이다! 들어가서 안전을 확보해!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원"], "content": "네! Fang 형님!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 P"], "content": "당신들...... 관리국 소속인가?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "음? 그럴 리가?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["electric bust", "전기 충격"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 P"], "content": "으아아아악! ....커헉...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "이제 네 녀석에게 볼일은 없다, 망할 짭X 놈. \n이 카드로 잠금을 푸는 건가?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "잠금 해제"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["범죄자 G"], "content": "오... 오오... 우리들을 구하러 와준 건가?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["범죄자 J"], "content": "다행이야......응! ? \n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 꺼낸다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "멋대로 움직이지 마. 머리에 바람 구멍 나기 싫으면 말이야.\n<font size=\"3.6\">알아 들었어!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["범죄자 G、범죄자 J"], "content": "네! 네 알겠습니다!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "아주 좋아.\n......Luis Pauline이 누구지?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......나다.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "잘됐군.\n......애들아, 어서 인사 올려라!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">안녕하십니까! 큰형님!</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......! ? \n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "놀래켜서 죄송합니다, 형님.\n저희는 형님을 구하러 왔습니다.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......아, 생각났군. 장례식에서 널 본 적이 있다. 하지만 넌 Baro의......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "이야기가 깁니다...... JOE가 어떤 제안을 내걸었고 모두가 그 제안에 동의했습니다. 현재 모든 조직들이 서로 협력하기로 하고 시민들을 위해서도 여러가지 일들을 준비하고 있습니다.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "! ? ......그런 일에 Diego가 동의했다고?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Diego는 이미 죽었습니다. 03의 Baro 지부에서.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......그런 거였군......\n그런데 어째서 나 같은 놈을 도와주려고 하는 거지?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "JOE, 그 녀석이 다음번에 있을 테러 사건을 예측하고 형님의 안전을 위해 우리들을 파견했습니다. 지금 바깥은 혼란 그 자체입니다. 자, 어서 서둘러야 합니다!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......아니, 난 이곳에 있겠다. 너희들은 돌아가라.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "형님... 이번 테러는 예전 규모와는 비교도 안됩니다. 어쩌면 이곳의 모든 시민들이 피난을 떠날 수도 있습니다. JOE의 부탁이기도 하고 이렇게 형님을 혼자 관제구역에 둘 수는 없습니다. \n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "그건...... 괜찮다.\nJOE에서 들었겠지? 난 살인자라고. Simon의 부친을 내 손으로 죽인.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "이곳에서 죽는 한이 있더라도 이곳에서 죄값을 받아야 하지. 내 딸도 하늘로 가버린 마당에, 그 아이와 빨리 만나는 것도 그리 나쁜 선택은 아니거든...\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "......그 Simon이라는 자도 이미 Node 08로 돌아와 적들과 교전 중이라고 합니다.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "! ? Simon이.....돌아왔다고?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "네, 아무래도 전력을 다해 이 모든 것을 끝내기로 결심한듯 합니다.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "형님, 저희 조직의 대부분 사람들은 크든 작든 범죄를 저지르며 살아왔습니다. 어떤 이들은 그 죄를 속죄할 기회조차 얻지 못하고 그저 후회 속에서만 살아가기도 합니다. 형님은 지금 죽어도 별로 상관이 없다고 생각할지도 모르지만, 그래도 살아있으면 그보다 더 가치있는 일을 해낼 수 있을 거라고...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......! \n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "형님? \n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "조심해!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "연사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[드론]"], "content": "<i>위협.....감지... <font size=\"1.6\">제거를.....</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "하아... 하아... 하아...\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "대... 대단하다... 순식간에 내 총을 빼앗고 바로 조준해서...\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "......JOE가 있는 곳으로 안내해.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "형님......드디어 마음을 돌리셨군요?\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "네 말대로, 나는 아직 죽지 않고 이렇게 살아있다. \n그러니 이 목숨... 누군가를 돕는 일에 사용하도록 하지.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[電視]"], "content": "<i>稍早於 Node 08 發生的攻擊事件，受災範圍已擴大到第二象限商業區，讓市民陷入巨大恐慌。除了越來越多無人機再度故障加入攻擊，不少目擊者亦指出，聚集在 A.R.C. 總部四周的人型機器人更加危險……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 G"], "content": "喂，這到底是怎麼回事？我們不會被攻擊吧？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 J"], "content": "快放我們走！我還不想死在這種地方！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "閉嘴！都給我安靜！否則有你們受的！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……。\n……？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "咳、咳，怎麼回……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>偵測到威脅，開始進行排除。</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "！？糟……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "搞定了，大家衝進去確保安全！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑幫人員"], "content": "是！Fang 哥！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "你們……是管理局的人嗎？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "哈？傻了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["electric bust", "電擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 P"], "content": "嗚啊啊啊啊！！……唔唔……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "沒你的事了，臭條子。這張卡就能開鎖了吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Arc_01", "開鎖"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 G"], "content": "喔、喔喔，是來救我們的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 J"], "content": "太好了……噫！？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "誰敢亂動，老子就崩掉誰的腦袋。\n<font size=\"3.6\">聽清楚了沒有！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["罪犯 G、罪犯 J"], "content": "是、是！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "很好。\n……我找 Luis Pauline，哪一位？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……是我。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "啊，太好了。\n……全體，敬禮！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["黑幫人員"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">是！大哥好！</font>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "驚擾大哥了，我們是來救大哥出去的。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……對了，我想起來了，喪禮那天我有見過你。但你是 Baro 的人……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "說來話長……JOE 提出了一個計畫，受到大家的認同。現在黑幫已經彼此合作，也準備為了一般市民做點事。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？……Diego 也同意？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "Diego 已經死了，死在 03 的 Baro 支部裡。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……是這樣嗎……\n那為什麼要來保護我這種人？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "JOE 那傢伙預測到會再有攻擊事件，才派我們來保護大哥安全。現在外面很混亂，我們得快點，來，和我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……不了，我待在這裡就好。你們回去吧。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥，這次攻擊和之前的規模不一樣，必要的話可能全體市民都得撤離。JOE 已經拜託我了，我不能讓大哥死在管制區裡頭……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "那也……沒關係。\nJOE 應該和你說了，我是個殺人犯。Simon 的父親就是死在我的手上。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "我罪有應得，就算死了也是一命償一命。何況現在女兒也走了，我下去就能和她團聚，沒什麼不好……\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "……JOE 和我說，那位 Simon 已經回到了 Node 08，正在與敵人交戰中。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "！？Simon 他……他回來了？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "是，看來他決定要全力阻止這一切發生。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥，我們黑幫的人多少都犯過一些錯，有些人甚至已經沒有贖罪的機會，只能後悔一輩子。也許大哥覺得死了也無所謂，但如果能用剩餘的一條爛命做到更多……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "小心！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[無人機]"], "content": "<i>偵測……到……<font size=\"1.6\">排除……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "呼、呼……呼……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "真厲害，一瞬間搶走我的槍並且瞄準……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……帶我去 JOE 那裡。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥……想通了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "就像你說的，我畢竟還活著。\n這條爛命……就用在幫助別人身上吧。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[电视]"], "content": "<i>稍早于 Node 08