ntent": "是，看来他决定要全力阻止这一切发生。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥，我们黑帮的人多少都犯过一些错，有些人甚至已经没有赎罪的机会，只能后悔一辈子。也许大哥觉得死了也无所谓，但如果能用剩余的一条烂命做到更多……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "小心！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "连续枪击"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[无人机]"], "content": "<i>侦测……到……<font size=\"1.6\">排除……</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "呼、呼……呼……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "真厉害，一瞬间抢走我的枪并且瞄准……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "……带我去 JOE 那里。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Fang"], "content": "大哥……想通了吗？\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Luis"], "content": "就像你说的，我毕竟还活着。\n这条烂命……就用在帮助别人身上吧。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}